description: Lightweight and highly scalable asynchronous WebSocket listener, compilant with the official RFC6455 specification. It supports async/await operations, SSL/TLS (wss://), message compression, customizable HTTP negotiation, built-in keep-alive, latency control, partial frames and have several extensibility points.
